  "title": "Structural Basis for Clonal Diversity of the Public T Cell Response to a Dominant Human Cytomegalovirus Epitope.",
  "journal": "The Journal of biological chemistry",
  "year": 2015,
  "authors": "Yang X, Gao M, Chen G, Pierce BG, Lu J, Weng NP, Mariuzza RA."
